Cook turkish/lebanese coffee in small cezve without sugar.

7 g of coffee, Espresso house Espresso blend
1,25 dl of warm water, 40 degrees Celsius or so.
Stir lightly
Cook on medium temperature until it boils up.
Let in sink again
Boil again
Let it sink again
Boil again
Let it sink
Let it cool down somewhat before using in chocolate.
